name: #3 Law of Action
description:
The Laws of Manifestation

#3 - Law of Action
Now here's where a lot of us go wrong, we think good things, and we hope that they'll arrive.

But it isn't as easy as that - you've got to put in the work so that the universe can help place opportunities in your path.

So start that piece of art, show the universe that you're willing to start working towards what you want.

Keep that energy moving, and you'll be surprised at what lands at your feet.

Everything you seek, it's already seeking you - it just wants to know that you're serious.
